power%2C%20and%20operate%20sustainable%20data%20centers.%20That%20starts%20with%20understanding%20emissions%20across%20the%20data%20center%20lifecycle.%20Design%20and%20construction%20impact%20embodied%20carbon%2C%20or%20the%20total%20amount%20of%20emissions%20associated%20with%20the%20data%20center%20lifecycle%2C%20from%20metal%20extraction%20to%20construction%2C%20all%20the%20way%20to%20equipment%20disposal.%20Operationally%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20electricity%20use.%20So%20we%20work%20closely%20with%20our%20energy%20procurement%20and%20strategy%20teams%20to%20decarbonize%20our%20electricity%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Scope%201%20emissions%2C%20referring%20to%20direct%20emissions%20from%20sources%20owned%20by%20our%20company%2C%20we're%20switching%20from%20burning%20mainly%20diesel%20in%20backup%20generators%20to%20renewable%20fuels%20like%20hydrotreated%20vegetable%20oil%2C%20a%20diesel-like%20fuel%20which%20we've%20deployed%20across%2017%25%20of%20our%20operating%20portfolio.%20But%2098%25%20of%20our%20Scope%201%20and%202%20emissions%2C%20which%20include%20the%20indirect%20emissions%20from%20purchased%20energy%2C%20come%20from%20electricity%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20big%20nut%20we%20need%20to%20crack.%20We%20prioritize%20opportunities%20based%20on%20where%20we%20can%20make%20the%20biggest%20impact%2C%20designing%20efficient%20facilities%20and%20powering%20them%20with%20renewables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKeon%3A%20I'd%20say%20on%20the%20Scope%203%20emissions%20side%2C%20which%20are%20indirect%20emissions%20from%20the%20data%20center%20supply%20chain%2C%20that's%20where%20my%20team%20can%20really%20have%20an%20impact.%20We're%20constantly%20working%20with%20our%20design%20and%20construction%20partners%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20specifying%20the%20right%20materials%20to%20help%20bring%20those%20emissions%20down.%20It's%20always%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20our%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20partner%20with%20Aaron's%20team%20during%20our%20annual%20business%20reviews%20with%20key%20suppliers.%20We%20just%20wrapped%20those%20up%20recently%2C%20and%20Scope%203%20emissions%20were%20one%20of%20the%20topics%20we%20discussed%20%E2%80%94%20how%20suppliers%20are%20performing%20and%20what%20we%20can%20do%20to%20improve.%20It's%20a%20never-ending%2C%20iterative%20process%2C%20but%20collaboration%20is%20key%20to%20making%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20models%20are%20creating%20a%20demand%20for%20computing%20power.%20How%20are%20you%20balancing%20this%20growth%20with%20your%20sustainability%20targets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBinkley%3A%20We've%20seen%20AI%20coming.%20It's%20front%20of%20mind%20now%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20our%20bookings%20are%20AI-related.%20Even%20as%20our%20portfolio%20grows%2C%20we%20haven't%20pulled%20back%20on%20any%20sustainability%20commitments.%20We've%20made%20strong%20progress%20on%20sourcing%20renewables%20and%20decarbonization.%20We%20plan%20for%20that%2C%20and%20as%20AI%20pushes%20greater%20demand%2C%20we%20adjust%20our%20plans%3A%20rethink%20sourcing%2C%20get%20more%20integrated%20with%20acquisitions%2C%20and%20get%20involved%20earlier%20in%20planning%20and%20design.%20We're%20even%20part%20of%20early%20utility%20conversations%20when%20acquiring%20land%2C%20asking%20for%20clean%20energy%20solutions%20before%20we've%20started%20moving%20dirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20also%20using%20AI%20internally%20to%20improve%20energy%20and%20water%20efficiency.%20We%20developed%20an%20in-house%20program%20called%20Apollo%20AI%20to%20optimize%20building%20management%20systems%20across%20our%20portfolio.%20The%20platform%20helps%20our%20facility%20engineers%20find%20hidden%20anomalies%20like%20clogged%20filters%20and%20leaky%20valves%20and%20suggests%20improvements%20that%20can%20help%20drive%20energy%20savings.%20We%20also%20have%20AI%20tools%20focused%20on%20water%20systems%2C%20helping%20us%20fine-tune%20cooling%20performance%20and%20water%20chemistry%20to%20reduce%20waste.%20We%20really%20try%20to%20squeeze%20every%20last%20drop%20of%20productivity%20out%20of%20the%20energy%20and%20water%20we%20consume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKeon%3A%20We're%20planning%20for%20100%25%20of%20our%20future%20buildings%20to%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20deploy%20liquid%20cooling%20directly%20to%20the%20chip%2C%20where%20coolant%20is%20circulated%20through%20metal%20plates%20attached%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egraphics%20processing%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20remove%20heat.%20For%20those%20that%20don't%2C%20our%20engineering%20team%20is%20building%20roadmaps%20so%20we're%20ready%20if%20customers%20want%20to%20use%20energy-intensive%20technologies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-reliant-on-big-tech-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20require%20high%20levels%20of%20compute%20power.%20Our%20modular%20design%20approach%20helps%20us%20learn%20and%20adapt%20quickly.%20And%20with%20liquid%20cooling%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20as%20much%20square%20footage%20per%20megawatt%20anymore.%20That's%20going%20to%20change%20how%20buildings%20are%20designed%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20in%20aligning%20technical%20engineering%20demands%20and%20sustainability%20goals%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBinkley%3A%20Our%20sustainability%20standards%20are%20part%20of%20our%20building%20codes%2C%20but%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20emissions%20that%20can%20be%20reduced%20in%20our%20facilities%20still%20varies%20based%20on%20customer%20usage.%20Some%20customers%20move%20into%20the%20data%20centers%20fully%20and%20operate%20at%20high%20intensity%3B%20others%20ramp%20up%20slowly.%20Modularity%20helps%20us%20handle%20those%20variations.%20The%20speed%20of%20growth%20is%20also%20a%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20we%20need%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20customer%20demand%2C%20line%20up%20renewables%2C%20and%20anticipate%20equipment%20needs%20that%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20procure.%20We're%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20takes%20years.%20You%20can't%20just%20flip%20a%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKeon%3A%20We're%20a%20multi-tenant%20facility.%20We%20lease%20out%20space%20to%20our%20customers%2C%20so%20while%20we%20control%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20customer%20ultimately%20controls%20how%20they%20operate%20within%20that%20space.%20We%20can%20design%20proactively%20with%20energy%20efficiency%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20we%20encourage%20best%20practices%20like%20airflow%20containment%20and%20optimal%20temperature%20settings.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20don't%20dictate%20how%20customers%20use%20their%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20creates%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20disconnect.%20Our%20engineering%20team%20can%20build%20in%20sustainability%20features%2C%20but%20our%20operations%20team%20has%20to%20be%20reactive%20depending%20on%20how%20each%20tenant%20deploys.%20Some%20customers%20come%20in%20and%20run%20at%20high%20utilization%2C%20which%20is%20great%20from%20an%20efficiency%20standpoint.%20Others%20move%20in%20slowly%20or%20use%20a%20mix%20of%20equipment%20that%20can%20affect%20how%20well%20the%20facility%20runs.%20So%20there's%20a%20line%20between%20what%20we%20can%20control%20and%20what%20we%20can%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20our%20operations%20team%20is%20very%20sophisticated.%20They%20use%20automation%2C%20data%2C%20and%20AI%20to%20adapt%20in%20real%20time%2C%20dialing%20in%20temperature%20and%20managing%20airflow%2C%20all%20to%20run%20as%20efficiently%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20how%20are%20you%20evolving%20your%20decarbonization%20strategy%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBinkley%3A%20We're%20not%20pulling%20back%20on%20our%20commitments.%20We'll%20stay%20the%20course%2C%20and%20perhaps%20even%20get%20more%20aggressive.%20Clean%20energy%20is%20harder%20to%20source%20now%2C%20but%20still%20available.%20We've%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20renewables%20that%20offer%20real%20value%20and%20reduce%20costs.%20We're%20also%20going%20deeper%20into%20Scope%203%20with%20our%20supplier%20engagement%20program%2C%20working%20with%20vendors%20to%20reduce%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20the%20materials%20and%20products%20we%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKeon%3A%20I'd%20echo%20that.%20Sustainability%20is%20embedded%20in%20our%20design%20process.%20It's%20not%20just%20a%20benchmark%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%20Our%20local%20teams%20are%20empowered%20to%20innovate%20project%20by%20project%2C%20and%20our%20global%20teams%20constantly%20share%20best%20practices.%20What%20works%20in%20France%20might%20be%20relevant%20in%20Chicago.%20It's%20a%20contagious%2C%20exciting%20environment%20to%20be%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-realty-ai-infrastructure-data-centers-sustainability-strategy-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749075620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683dcbc5c6ad288d14825067%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-realty-ai-infrastructure-data-centers-sustainability-strategy-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20data%20centers%20consume%20a%20lot%20of%20energy%20and%20water.%20At%20Digital%20Realty%2C%20collaboration%20is%20key%20to%20driving%20business%20while%20meeting%20sustainability%20goals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amok%40insider.com%20(Aaron%20Mok)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-realty-ai-infrastructure-data-ce