nize%20their%20operations%20with%20technology%2C%20including%20their%20accounting%20systems%20and%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Chase%20said%20more%20clients%20have%20sought%20assistance%20in%20incorporating%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20cloud%20services%20into%20their%20digital%20transformation%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%2C%20KPMG%20announced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpmg.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fkpmg-google-cloud-partnership-expansion-2024.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpansion%20of%20its%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-cloud-platform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Cloud%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20to%20advance%20GenAI%2C%20data%20analytics%2C%20and%20cybersecurity%20for%20its%20clients.%20The%20expansion%20includes%20a%20%24100%20million%20investment%20in%20KPMG's%20Google%20Cloud%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20tailor%20AI%20services%20to%20specific%20customers%2C%20business%20models%2C%20and%20industries%20so%20that%20these%20organizations%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20their%20businesses%2C%20such%20as%20by%20speeding%20up%20data%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expanded%20Google%20Cloud%20partnership%20will%20initially%20focus%20on%20clients%20in%20the%20retail%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20financial%20services%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Chase%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684076219d73a0031e8ddb2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteve%20Chase%20is%20the%20vice%20chair%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20digital%20innovation%20at%20KPMG.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20KPMG%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e37fe46f-2412-4f7e-b9e7-dfdfd5a980a8%5C%22%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20said%20KPMG%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20for%20several%20years%20and%20has%20had%20a%20long-standing%20relationship%20with%20Google.%20In%202024%2C%20KPMG%20created%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpmg.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fkpmg-google-cloud-responsible-ai-2024.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Cloud%20Center%20of%20Excellence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20combine%20Google's%20AI%20technologies%20with%20its%20own%20expertise%20to%20help%20clients%20use%20AI%20to%20boost%20their%20businesses.%20Its%20latest%20partnership%20expansion%20involves%20creating%20new%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20also%20works%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-microsoft-teaming-to-bring-more-ai-workplace-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20and%20other%20tech%20companies%20on%20other%20AI-related%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225010844e-835d-4db4-9246-59f4063935bd%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20Action%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-boss-david-rowlands-artificial-intelligence-strategy-big-four-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKPMG%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20using%20Google%20Cloud's%20Vertex%20AI%20Search%2C%20an%20AI%20development%20platform%20for%20building%20and%20using%20GenAI%2C%20internally%20to%20connect%20and%20analyze%20its%20vast%20amount%20of%20data.%20Chase%20said%20the%20company%20is%20using%20this%20information%20to%20develop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGenAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20clients%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20answer%20questions%20or%20tools%20to%20gather%20and%20analyze%20data%2C%20to%20address%20various%20business%20challenges%20and%20expand%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Chase%20said%20KPMG%20is%20using%20Vertex%20AI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Google%20Cloud%20AI-powered%20assistant%2C%20to%20help%20financial%20services%20companies%20automate%20tasks%20that%20have%20been%20cumbersome%20for%20humans%2C%20including%20fraud%20detection%20and%20loan%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20added%20that%20KPMG%20also%20built%20an%20AI%20%26quot%3Bstore%20performance%20analyzer%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20large%20retailer.%20The%20tool%20allows%20the%20company%20to%20use%20automation%20to%20speed%20up%20and%20combine%20information%20from%20store%20locations%2C%20such%20as%20inventory%20levels%2C%20sales%20data%2C%20and%20details%20about%20the%20location%2C%20to%20determine%20how%20it%20performs%20compared%20to%20other%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20able%20to%20actually%20do%20a%20detailed%20analysis%20in%20a%20fast%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20used%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20a%20team%20of%20people%20and%20take%20longer%2C%20Chase%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20people%20involved%20are%20actually%20reviewing%20the%20results%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20doing%20all%20the%20manual%20work%20of%20pulling%20all%20the%20data%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-healthcare-doctors-drugs-treatments-patients-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20clients%2C%20KPMG%20is%20using%20Google%20Cloud's%20Healthcare%20API%20to%20develop%20AI%20tools%20that%20help%20doctors%20improve%20disease%20detection%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20overall%20patient%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d41eabb-4c8a-4921-8b4e-f62ada71c567%5C%22%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20said%20that%20KPMG's%20partnership%20with%20Google%20Cloud%20could%20drive%20%241%20billion%20incremental%20growth%20for%20the%20firm.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20super%20pleased%20with%20how%20it's%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20said%20the%20company%20couldn't%20disclose%20specifics%20on%20how%20it'll%20reach%20this%20figure%2C%20he%20said%20it%20will%20be%20a%20multi-year%20initiative%20that%20involves%20adding%20new%20clients%20and%20expanding%20the%20AI%20services%20it%20offers%20to%20existing%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20continues%20to%20roll%20out%20new%20AI%20initiatives.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpmg.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fkpmg-google-cloud-alliance-expansion-agentspace-adoption.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpansion%20of%20its%20collaboration%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Google%20Cloud%20on%20AI%20tools%20for%20the%20legal%20and%20banking%20industries.%20KPMG%20also%20announced%20that%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpmg.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fkpmg-joins-google-cloud-security-program.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoining%20the%20Google%20Cloud%20Security%20Partner%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20enhance%20cybersecurity%20for%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-automation-services-for-clients-drive-revenue-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749074835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840b8edc19ab3675c10ab1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-automation-services-for-clients-drive-revenue-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KPMG%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Big%2