%20defenses%20at%20bases%2C%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20has%20been%20on%20missiles%2C%20but%20drones%20come%20with%20a%20different%20set%20of%20problems.%20To%20protect%20against%20drones%2C%20it%20isn't%20enough%20to%20fortify%20shelters.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20any%20openings%2C%26quot%3B%20Cancian%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20have%20a%20roof%20and%20then%20an%20open%20front%20because%20they'll%20just%20fly%20in.%26quot%3B%20One%20solution%20he%20said%20may%20start%20to%20appear%20is%20a%20mesh%20structure%20or%20curtain%20for%20those%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225662%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20B-2%20Spirit%20stealth%20bomber%20flying%20above%20the%20clouds%20with%20two%20stealth%20fighter%20aircraft%20on%20either%20side%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e270a4bf0250c2149291e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20bombers%2C%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20other%20aircraft%20would%20be%20high-value%20targets%20in%20a%20war%20with%20China.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Senior%20Airman%20Samantha%20White%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20recent%20strike%20on%20Russian%20airpower%20could%20be%20just%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20such%20a%20future%20attack%20could%20look%20like%2C%20experts%20said.%20Sunday's%20attack%2C%20Walton%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3Bwas%20in%20the%20form%20of%20quadcopters%3B%20in%20the%20future%2C%20it%20could%20be%20similar%20drones%20but%20with%20even%20greater%20autonomy%2C%20small%2C%20low-cost%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20or%20other%20weapons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20potential%20targets%20could%20grow%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpiderweb%20demonstrated%20something%20that%20military%20experts%20and