tive%2C%20and%20time-consuming.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20humans%20working%20in%20the%20background%20for%20these%20doctors%20and%20providers%20who%20help%20them%20do%20their%20non-clinical%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20said%20Omega%20Healthcare%20wanted%20to%20automate%20billing%2C%20insurance%20claims%2C%20and%20other%20administrative%20tasks%20to%20free%20up%20employees%20to%20handle%20decision-making%20aspects%2C%20such%20as%20when%20to%20deny%20claims%20or%20follow%20up%20on%20a%20late%20payment.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20improve%20its%20operations%20and%20help%20its%20clients%20increase%20collections%2C%20minimize%20incorrect%20claim%20submissions%20and%20denial%20rates%2C%20reduce%20receivable%20payment%20times%2C%20and%20enhance%20patient%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222679%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rajusiva%20Arunachalam%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f7cb6ca50259add4cd478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222009%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERajusiva%20Arunachalam%20is%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20technology%20at%20Omega%20Healthcare.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Omega%20Healthcare%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c30d2f0-becd-41e6-9999-e9e9f0f03ce3%5C%22%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOmega%20Healthcare%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fin%2Fnews-releases%2Fomega-healthcare-processes-60-million-transactions-with-enterprise-ai-and-automation-from-uipath-302285442.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartnered%20with%20UiPath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20enterprise%20automation%20and%20AI%20software%20company%2C%20about%20five%20years%20ago%20to%20automate%20some%20of%20the%20workers'%20manual%20administrative%20tasks%2C%20including%20billing%2C%20medical%20coding%2C%20and%20correspondence%20with%20insurance%20companies.%20Arunachalam%20said%20UiPath's%20platform%20was%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20Omega%20Healthcare's%20strategy%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20boosting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-powerhouses-betting-on-healthcare-ai-amazon-nvidia-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautomation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20speeding%20up%20the%20completion%20of%20clients'%20administrative%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20said%20Omega%20Healthcare%20created%20an%20internal%20team%20made%20up%20of%20developers%2C%20business%20analysts%2C%20and%20data%20scientists.%20The%20group%20focused%20on%20finding%20opportunities%20to%20automate%20repetitive%20tasks%20to%20save%20employees'%20time%20while%20speeding%20up%20work%20for%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22229114cd-ead5-48c6-8c84-648583fa02bb%5C%22%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOmega%20Healthare%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uipath.com%2Fresources%2Fautomation-case-studies%2Fomega-healthcare-boosts-efficiency-through-automation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euses%20UiPath%20Document%20Understanding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI%20tool%20that%20automatically%20pulls%20data%20from%20various%20client%20documents%2C%20such%20as%20accounts%20receivable%20correspondence%2C%20insurance%20denial%20letters%2C%20or%20electronic%20medical%20records.%20Arunachalam%20said%20the%20AI%20tool%20extracts%20data%20from%20these%20documents%20based%20on%20what%20a%20healthcare%20institution%20is%20trying%20to%20accomplish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20the%20task%20is%20to%20file%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-using-ai-to-disrupt-healthcare-insurance-payment-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einsurance%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20AI%20tool%20may%20pull%20out%20relevant%20data%20from%20electronic%20medical%20records.%20Or%2C%20if%20a%20claim%20was%20denied%2C%20it%20may%20identify%20relevant%20data%20from%20a%20denial%20letter%20or%20transcript%20of%20a%20call%20about%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20said%20human%20staff%20members%20review%20the%20data%20extracted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hospital-inventory-management-advice-mayo-clinic-cleveland-clinic-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20use%20it%20to%20make%20decisions.%20For%20instance%2C%20they%20may%20decide%20that%20a%20claim%20was%20denied%20incorrectly%20due%20to%20a%20medical%20coding%20problem%20or%20based%20on%20information%20from%20a%20medical%20record.%20Staff%20can%20also%20use%20the%20tool%20to%20follow%20up%20with%20a%20healthcare%20company%20for%20more%20information%20on%20a%20billing%20error.%20Employees%20then%20send%20their%20decision%20to%20the%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuman%20work%20is%20now%20more%20knowledge-based%2C%20very%20decision-oriented%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20AI%20technology%20can't%20do%2C%20Arunachalam%20said.%20But%20humans%20and%20AI%20%26quot%3Bwork%20together%20in%20conjunction%20to%20achieve%20what%20the%20client%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20%26quot%3Bcan%20run%2024%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Arunachalam%20said.%20It%20can%20also%20process%20data%20much%20faster%2C%20so%20fewer%20employees%20are%20needed%20for%20this%20work%2C%20which%20is%20more%20cost-effective%20for%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20added%20that%20Omega%20Healthcare%20has%20automated%20its%20administrative%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20submitting%20insurance%20claims%20and%20medical%20billing%2C%20for%20about%2060%25%20to%2070%25%20of%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22240fcd32-b3e9-4b92-bc31-5ff918f5ecf6%5C%22%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20Omega%20Healthcare%20has%20processed%20more%20than%20100%20million%20transactions%20using%20UiPath%20automations%2C%20Arunachalam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmega%20Healthcare%20tracked%20the%20time%20it%20took%20employees%20to%20manually%20complete%20different%20administrative%20tasks%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20time%20they%20spent%20on%20them%20after%20adding%20UiPath's%20tool%20to%20measure%20the%20tech's%20impact.%20Arunachalam%20said%20the%20company%20found%20that%20automation%20was%20saving%20employees%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20hours%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20said%20Omega%20Healthcare%20has%20also%20reduced%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20workers%20spend%20on%20documentation%20tasks%20by%2040%25.%20He%20added%20that%20automation%20has%20also%20slashed%20document%20processing%20turnaround%20time%20by%2050%25%20with%20a%20process%20accuracy%20of%2099.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20told%20BI%20that%20these%20improvements%20have%20increased%20efficiency%20and%20cost%20savings%20for%20Omega%20Healthcare's%20clients%2C%20delivering%20a%2030%25%20return%20on%20investment%20since%20using%20the%20AI-powered%20automation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArunachalam%20said%20Omega%20Healthcare%20is%20working%20on%20automating%20more%20of%20its%20client%20work%2C%20including%20payment%20posting%20and%20patient%20appointment%20scheduling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomega-healthcare-uipath-ai-document-processing-health-transactions-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749060943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f4f299b2a601d01b23b30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomega-healthcare-uipath-ai-document-processing-health-transactions-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20revenue%20cycle%20management%20company%20partnered%20with%20UiPath%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20automate%20administrative%20tasks%2C%20like%20medical%20billing%2C%20saving%20employees%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40ins